DESIGN UI DOCUMENTATION - AbsenKu Green Theme Application
===========================================
APLIKASI ABSENSI KARYAWAN
Green Theme - Modern Dashboard
===========================================

1. WARNA PALETTE
Warna hijau yang dipilih: Emerald-Teal Fusion — terkesan profesional, modern, dan segar. Bukan hijau stabilo, tapi hijau gelap elegan dengan aksen teal.
Primary Colors (Green Theme)
NameHex CodeUsagePrimary#10B981Main accent, buttons, highlightsPrimary Light#34D399Hover states, secondary accentsPrimary Dark#059669Sidebar gradient top, darker elementsSecondary#047857Text accents
