4. SHADOWS
Light Mode Shadows
--shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(16 185 129 / 0.05);
--shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1);
--shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1);
--shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.1);
Dark Mode Shadows
--shadow-sm: 0 1px 2px 0 rgb(16 185 129 / 0.2);
--shadow-md: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.3), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.3);
--shadow-lg: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.4), 0 4px 6px -4px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.4);
--shadow-xl: 0 20px 25px -5px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.5), 0 8px 10px -6px rgb(16 185 129 / 0.5);

5. BUTTONS
Primary Button
css.btn-primary {
  background-color: var(--primary); /* #10B981 */
  color: white;
  padding: 0.625rem 1.25rem;
  border-radius: var(--radius-md); /* 10px */
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}
.btn-primary:hover {
  background-color: var(--primary-light); /* #34D399 */
  transform: translateY(-1px);
  box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
}
Ghost Button
css.btn-ghost {
  background-color: transparent;
  color: var(--text-secondary);
}
.btn-ghost:hover {
  background-color: var(--primary-soft); /* rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) */
  color: var(--primary);
}

6. INPUT FIELDS
Standard Input
css.input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
  border: 2px solid var(--border-color); /* #D1FAE5 */
  border-radius: var(--radius-md); /* 10px */
  background-color: var(--surface);
  color: var(--text-primary);
  font-family: inherit;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
  outline: none;
}
.input:focus {
  border-color: var(--primary); /* #10B981 */
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px var(--primary-soft); /* rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1) */
}

7. LOGIN PAGE DESIGN
Layout: Centered Single Card

Background: Animated gradient with floating blobs
Card Position: Centered vertically and horizontally
Card Style: Glassmorphism (backdrop-filter blur)

Login Card Specifications
Width: max-width 480px
Padding: 3rem
Border Radius: 24px
Background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95)
Shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25)
Backdrop Blur: 20px
Animated Background
1. Gradient Animation
   - Colors: #10b981, #047857, #34d399, #059669, #022c22
   - Animation: 15s ease infinite
   - Movement: 400% 400% background-size

2. Floating Blobs (4 blobs)
   - Blob 1: 400x400px, #10b981, top:-100px, left:-100px
   - Blob 2: 300x300px, #34d399, bottom:-50px, right:-50px
   - Blob 3: 200x200px, #047857, top:50%, left:30%
   - Blob 4: 250x250px, #022c22, top:20%, right:20%
   - All blobs: filter blur(80px), opacity 0.4
   - Animation: blobFloat 20s ease-in-out infinite

3. Grid Overlay
   - Background: linear-gradient lines (50px x 50px)
   - Color: rgba(255,255,255,0.03)
Logo Section
Container: 100px x 100px, centered
Icon Box: 40px x 40px, 15px inset, border-radius 20px
Background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%)
Shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.4)
SVG Icon: 40px x 40px, white stroke

Animations:
- .logo-ring: border 3px #10b981, border-radius 24px, pulse 3s
- .logo-pulse: border 2px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.3), border-radius 32px, scale pulse

Title (App Name):
- Font: Quicksand, 1.75rem, weight 800
- Background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%)
- -webkit-background-clip: text
- -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent

Tagline:
- Font: Quicksand, 0.875rem, weight 500
- Color: #6b7280 (gray)
Login Form
Input Modern:
- Padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3rem (left for icon)
- Border: 2px solid #f3f4f6
- Border Radius: 12px
- Focus: border-color #10b981, box-shadow 0 0 0 4px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.15)
- Icon: 20px x 20px, position absolute left 1rem

Login Button:
- Width: 100%
- Padding: 1rem 2rem
- Background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981 0%, #047857 100%)
- Border Radius: 12px
- Font: Quicksand, 1rem, weight 700, white
- Shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.35)
- Hover: transform translateY(-2px), shadow 0 15px 40px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.45)
Quick Access Buttons
Container: flex, gap 0.75rem, margin-bottom 1.5rem

Button Style:
- Padding: 0.75rem 1rem
- Background: #f0fdf9
- Border: 2px solid #d1fae5
- Border Radius: 10px
- Color: #047857
- Font: Quicksand, 0.8rem, weight 700
- Icon: 24px x 24px
- Hover: background #10b981, color white, transform translateY(-2px)

8. SIDEBAR DESIGN
Sidebar Container
Width: 280px (expanded), 80px (collapsed)
Background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(--primary-dark) 0%, var(--primary) 100%)
   Light: #059669 → #10B981
   Dark: #064E3B → #065F46
Color: white
Position: fixed left
Z-Index: 50
Shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1)
Sidebar Header
Padding: 2rem (p-8)
Border Bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05)
Flex: items-center, justify-between, gap 1rem

Logo Box:
- Width/Height: 48px x 48px
- Background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1)
- Border Radius: 12px
- Backdrop Blur: present
- Font: Quicksand, 1.25rem, weight 800, italic
- Color: #6EE7B7 (text-emerald-200)

App Name:
- Font: Quicksand, 1rem, weight 800
- Color: white + accent color #6EE7B7
Navigation Menu Item (Sidebar Link)
css.sidebar-link {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  padding: 0.875rem 1.5rem;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
  font-weight: 500;
  font-size: 0.875rem;
  border-left: 4px solid transparent;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
  width: 100%;
  background: transparent;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
}
.sidebar-link:hover {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  color: white;
}
.sidebar-link.active {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
  color: white;
  border-left-color: #ECFDF5;
}
Text Color - BRIGHT WHITE VISIBILITY
Default: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7)
Hover: white
Active: white

class="sidebar-text text-white font-semibold"

